org.eclipse.wst.xml.xpath.core.internal.model.XPath.Function
Interface FunctionPackage.Literals

Enclosing interface:
FunctionPackage
public static interface FunctionPackage.Literals

Defines literals for the meta objects that represent

  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type
